-- Chavez Says He Will Return to Cuba Late Saturday
-- B y   C o r i n a   P o n s
-- 2012-04-07T01:11:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-07/chavez-says-he-will-return-to-cuba-late-saturday.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
speaking by phone on state television, said he will depart for
Cuba tomorrow for further treatment for his undisclosed cancer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corina Pons in Caracas at 
